name: Swimmy Bird
description:
Game producer - Kelsey Monteath

Programmer - Sean Beyer

Artist - Charlie Renwick

This game was made at Global Game Jam 2017. It was all of our first game jams and it needed to be finished in 48 hours. We didn't get everything finished that we would of liked, but it was a playable game and we are very proud of how it turned out.
